title: Lana Jewelry Gold Loop Hoop
description:
Take a fresh twist on a traditional hoop. Both feminine and flirty, these hoops exude undeniable confidence.  Made of 14-karat gold.  Designed by Chicago designer and founder of the luxe jewelry line Lana Jewelry, Lana Bramlette.   Go glam and channel your inner celebrity! 

1 1/2 in.
